description:
&lt;p&gt;The StaffBank for Epsom and St Helier NHS Trust is seeking experienced Phlebotomists to work in the Phlebotomy Department at St Helier and Epsom Hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note, you are required to have extensive recent experience in this role as we do not offer training. You will be assessed by the department before you can start working.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working hours are between 08.30 - 17.00, Monday to Friday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* please note this is a flexible position and is not a permanent role. Shifts will be adhoc *&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Current, clean driving licence and access to a car is also beneficial.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
